gomodel:SYNGO_66  a       owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Using an PKC-gamma specific antibody with knock out control, it is demonstrated that PKC gamma is expressed in the presynaptic terminal of the Calyx of Held.\n\n3/2/2017 Pim:\n-The cytosol term is derived from knowledge of the activity cycle of PKCgamma (see expert comments).. Experimental description: PKCγ KO mice (Abeliovich et al., 1993) were obtained from Jackson Laboratory." ;
